What beautiful music. One doesn't have to be a Muslim or religious, one doesn't have to be from Pakistan, India, or Afghanistan to appreciate the music and the soul of the singer. Who knows, you might even enjoy this poem: LISTEN TO THE MUSIC OF THE WIND IN PAKISTAN. If you know someone who speaks fluent English and Urdu, someone who would be good at translating this poem into URDU, please let me know: henrikeger@gmail.com SHUKRIA.
